#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:42 41b39079cc464605a72a4786bf6e923d
msgid "中英版本唤醒/命令固件支持自学习吗？"
msgstr "Do the Chinese and English wake-word/command firmware versions support self-learning?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:43 ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:74 3e2857e70c034f4aba984a6fd3a8af1a 60becd37584445d6b38d7b5bd026a6a0
msgid "支持"
msgstr "Yes."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:47 89e0a912b9354d3d969a3274b69897b0
msgid "支持粤语/河南话等方言吗？"
msgstr "Are Cantonese, Henan dialect, and other dialects supported?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:48 c215ba5fc1fe4f45b2ba706843b879bb
msgid "不支持"
msgstr "No."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:52 1a995452e1be4935be27cf420c8b2ce2
msgid "VC系列和之前的VB系列语音模组，开发环境/下载器是一样的吗？"
msgstr "Are the development environment and downloader for the VC series the same as those for the previous VB series voice modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:53 ef320b58702044fc83211df7124cf472
msgid "VC使用开发平台是Linux ,VB是Windows CDK IDE，各自有自己的下载器下载"
msgstr "VC uses a Linux development platform, while VB uses the Windows CDK IDE. Each has its own downloader."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:57 68e7bd6f375741cd8353977dc6e34e5c
msgid "VC系列模组接麦克风推荐购买哪种"
msgstr "What type of microphone is recommended for VC series modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:58 d95328837cd24fc4b0b49d9c71a38dc7
msgid "可以按照灵敏度-27db的标准"
msgstr "You can choose one according to the sensitivity standard of -27 dB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:61 dd70085a21424245ba5ff863b90edd9b
msgid "VC系列模组咪头的拾音最远能达到多少米"
msgstr "What is the maximum pickup distance of the microphone on VC series modules?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:62 37ee549b044e46bfbff0b22424deb506
msgid "最远5米。"
msgstr "Up to 5 meters."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:65 4ce8ad9525b649898f83c88fb8898617
msgid "VC系列模组支持播报吗"
msgstr "Do VC series modules support voice announcements?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:66 6bc8afd30c5a409a87e8b2305206b22b
msgid "支持，不过没有TTS功能"
msgstr "Yes, but they do not have TTS functionality."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:69 9d7f18a6f8ae442a997853ee2f4ec581
msgid "VC系列模组使用语音开放平台是不能进入I2C开发吗？"
msgstr "Does using the voice open platform mean the VC series module cannot enter I2C development?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:70 ae8be89a6cda4c3c8155722441770d9c
msgid "不能开发I2C功能"
msgstr "I2C functionality cannot be developed."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:73 2ad99fbc74224a80b543493d38181386
msgid "VC系列模组支持自定义免唤醒命令词吗"
msgstr "Do VC series modules support custom wake-free command words?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:77 e81a74415ff9471c8fa13e729ab1c1bc
msgid "VC系列开发板中文固件和英文固件是不是硬件通用的"
msgstr "Are the Chinese firmware and English firmware for the VC series development board compatible with the same hardware?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:78 ec2bc4eaba5c48e998a3c3817863a6b3
msgid "共用同一个硬件"
msgstr "They use the same hardware."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:81 a3e8a88b7a6941558d831f918512c8f2
msgid "VC模组在线创建产品SDK中有B2B3B6B7引脚，但是实际产品引脚定义没有这几个引脚，是怎么回事"
msgstr "In the SDK created online for VC modules, there are B2, B3, B6, and B7 pins, but the actual product pin definition does not include these pins. Why?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:82 c548f7eb64f8417d88d974282a5e9e82
msgid "B0 B1 B8 是特殊功能脚，B8是系统log 默认是输出脚波特率57600，B0 B1是JATG 烧录脚"
msgstr "B0, B1, and B8 are special function pins. B8 is the system log pin and is an output pin by default with a baud rate of 57600. B0 and B1 are JTAG programming pins."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:85 6004ea7a63f94dec90867b260fcf8b2c
msgid "VC系列所使用的咪头参数是多少"
msgstr "What are the microphone parameters used by the VC series?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:86 a7ea479a228543b68c8a627d353045ac
msgid "咪头的接收灵敏度为-31dB"
msgstr "The microphone receiving sensitivity is -31 dB."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:89 4fdb007e478f41bd8dbe1ef106d68aa0
msgid "VC-02模块支持永久唤醒吗"
msgstr "Does the VC-02 module support permanent wake-up?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:90 028920a6c8b6453b82046804dd6273cf
msgid "支持，需要通过开发实现，出厂固件没有实现该功能"
msgstr "Yes. It needs to be implemented through development. The factory firmware does not implement this function."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:93 bb7e4a04ff3d4550aa2d05bef2a25483
msgid "请问VC语音开发板的串口是哪一种芯片？"
msgstr "What chip is used for the serial port on the VC voice development board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:94 5e56ca823278433d97744717a8201023
msgid "CH340"
msgstr "CH340."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:97 28036e2977ee416189910299705dec86
msgid "VC-02-Kit是否可以用于驱动舵机？"
msgstr "Can the VC-02-Kit be used to drive a servo?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:98 eb0dc0305de64ffcac75f62ea11cfe8f
msgid "需外部搭建H桥等电路配合驱动"
msgstr "An external H-bridge or similar circuit is required for driving it."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:101 4b26abd3d8aa4fcabe386cf4bfb52bf2
msgid "目前有哪些模块支持声纹识别功能"
msgstr "Which modules currently support voiceprint recognition?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:102 be61a5a2a4b84e0499a26c80d8eb0bbc
msgid "声纹识别功能的模块目前没有，有语音识别的VC系列模块"
msgstr "There are currently no modules with voiceprint recognition. The VC series modules support voice recognition."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:105 fb209cbd199d42e395c0d2a0ad63a44f
msgid "VC开发板是否可以通过板子上的USB口进行固件烧录"
msgstr "Can the VC development board burn firmware through the USB port on the board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:106 6ae7bf5df7e246a5929a0609f1b8e2d5
msgid "可以，模块通过USB转串口的方式给开发板进行固件烧写(烧录的固件必须使用build.sh update指令生成的uni_app_release_update.bin,烧录工具只能使用UniOneUpdateTool.exe)"
msgstr "Yes. The module uses USB-to-serial to burn firmware to the development board. The firmware to be burned must be the ``uni_app_release_update.bin`` generated by the ``build.sh update`` command, and the burning tool can only be ``UniOneUpdateTool.exe``."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:109 4bfcd50a217d4fdbba81f006d1640a80
msgid "VC-02的命令词可以自己编辑吗"
msgstr "Can the command words of VC-02 be edited by users?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:110 1f23fe01a6534391b2d9b60b706eeba4
msgid "可以，通过平台生成SDK的方式"
msgstr "Yes. This can be done by generating an SDK through the platform."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:113 6a6095c0911f438c8d7fbfe29c3153cd
msgid "VC-02开发板可以同时识别英文和中文吗"
msgstr "Can the VC-02 development board recognize English and Chinese at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:114 45477250efdf4fff974bcb2fe3e5bf4b
msgid "不可以，烧写什么版本的固件就支持什么语言"
msgstr "No. It supports whichever language version of firmware is burned."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:117 ef2f2694bfde483bac6ab75532c660dd
msgid "VC-01中文和英文能做到一起使用吗"
msgstr "Can VC-01 support Chinese and English at the same time?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:118 ba3f025b8f774ec29ef5fa959b543abb
msgid "不可以，中文固件和英文固件只能二选一"
msgstr "No. Chinese firmware and English firmware are mutually exclusive; only one can be selected."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:121 e2a7dfd8183d4673bdcf9849c6bd7cea
msgid "请问VC-02-Kit是要自己写代码么？还是给一个网页，设置完了以后生成bin文件？"
msgstr "For VC-02-Kit, do users need to write code themselves, or is there a web page where settings are configured and then a bin file is generated?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:122 ba6d39a0db36457191f94fed5729a4f6
msgid "网页设置完成将生成对应功能的SDK，用户直接SDK编译完成后生成固件，也可在SDK的功能做一些完善之后再编译生成固件"
msgstr "After configuration on the web page, an SDK with the corresponding functions will be generated. Users can directly compile the SDK to generate firmware, or improve the SDK functions before compiling and generating firmware."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:125 3a280093edae4295a99131920702977c
msgid "VC-02离线语音模组可以使用arduinoIDE编程吗"
msgstr "Can the VC-02 offline voice module be programmed with Arduino IDE?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:126 4d339b97a9f94fca99ab545ab8174764
msgid "不可以，目前仅支持通过语音平台生成的SDK进行编程"
msgstr "No. Currently, it only supports programming through the SDK generated by the voice platform."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:129 1d5c226be44b4395ab72a961b8925744
msgid "VC-02开发板做开发的时候注册账号，下载离线语音固件需要收费吗"
msgstr "When developing with the VC-02 development board, is there any charge for registering an account or downloading offline voice firmware?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:130 f0a3c0d97e1c4702be9a9f17bf336b60
msgid "不需要收费，注册账号和下载固件都是免费的"
msgstr "No. Account registration and firmware downloads are both free."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:133 b61c4e7650c448beb8ab6b0d4768e9da
msgid "请问贵司有支持语音对话，并且可以对接云端的模组么？"
msgstr "Do you have any modules that support voice conversation and cloud connection?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:134 74126c40bc8d4f4daff03f4adb1b2447
msgid "目前没有支持语音对话的模组；"
msgstr "Currently, there are no modules that support voice conversation."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:137 e9baa812ec6b4875947d7a18edab626a
msgid "VC系列模组通过在线生成离线语音估计，只有一个文件，没有update格式的问题该如何处理"
msgstr "When generating offline voice firmware online for VC series modules, only one file is generated and there is no update-format file. How should this be handled?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:138 d89b09b68ee14d9d8f3e542254177223
msgid "使用./build.sh update，编译的时候后缀带update才会有"
msgstr "Use ``./build.sh update``. The update-format file will only be generated when the compilation command includes ``update``."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:141 62decb730bd84820b2cadef64c3b0037
msgid "VC-02开发板配套的喇叭是多少欧姆多少W的"
msgstr "What are the impedance and power rating of the speaker supplied with the VC-02 development board?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:142 5ac2dd41e6964287ab4c9f6777e77d4d
msgid "2W8欧姆"
msgstr "2W, 8 ohms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:145 348ca1d1e9e74f799ebdf8d87198909a
msgid "VC-02开发板支持休眠状态下进行语音唤醒吗"
msgstr "Does the VC-02 development board support voice wake-up in sleep mode?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:146 db90968f579840e786df12863d900498
msgid "不支持休眠状态进行语音唤醒，目前仅支持待机状态进行语音唤醒"
msgstr "It does not support voice wake-up in sleep mode. Currently, voice wake-up is only supported in standby mode."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:149 0404fc3c4f8d4c919a0a4b646597874d
msgid "VC-02开发板可以录音吗"
msgstr "Can the VC-02 development board record audio?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:150 82ba029c390149cd9976d36b8b5a3c1b
msgid "不可以，开发板没有录音功能"
msgstr "No. The development board does not have a recording function."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:153 b3eb9f3d1b38457591c690bde6bfd6d8
msgid "VC离线语音模组支持OTA吗"
msgstr "Does the VC offline voice module support OTA?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:154 91b9cbf6487744ce98534d4d9dc8bb38
msgid "不支持，模组本身没有这个功能"
msgstr "No. The module itself does not have this function."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:157 c107f153324c46698103cbce7d672069
msgid "请问离线语音模组输出能驱动几路继电器呢？"
msgstr "How many relay channels can the offline voice module output drive?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/VC/index.rst:158 a589fe43041640b899e21dfcb0bcd2ba
msgid "4"
msgstr "4."
